summary: Hey hey hey! @taylorswift me and my bff @northernisms are coming to see you in 16 DAYS BABY. 16 DAYS!!!!!!!! I. CAN. NOT. WAIT....
body:
HEY TAY. 💖

Hey hey hey! @taylorswift me and my bff @northernisms are coming to see you in 16 DAYS BABY. 16 DAYS!!!!!!!! I. CAN. NOT. WAIT.

The last time we saw you together was Fearless 2009, so it’s gonna be HELLA emotional. I’m not ready. We saw your mum that day and we were so shocked that I couldn’t even shout her name, I ended up SCREECHING and shouting “mommmmaaaaa! Mommmaaa Swift”

Not my finest moment, luckily she didn’t see us 😂🙈


This show looks absolutely incredible and I can’t wait to hear all the songs and see your beautiful face stare into the crowd as we sing along and scream at the top of our lungs. I can’t wait to dance the night away, it’s going to phenomenal.

Thank you for all the effort that’s been put into this tour for us tay, it’s just out of this world. All the videos, the stage, how imitate it is, the behind the scenes we don’t see, the time you spend before AND after with us it’s just amazing. You are the most kindest, sweetest person in the world and I’d just like to say thank you for everything you’ve done for us.

And thank you for everything you’ve done for me, you’ve no idea how much you’ve helped me but you honestly have. Through the most hardest times in my life and the best, thank you from the bottom of my heart. I’ll stand by you forever and always tay 💖


(IM NOW ALSO COMING ON NIGHT TWO IN MANCHESTER WITH MY BABY WHO’S FLY LIKE A JETSTREAM!!!!)

summary: It’s been really fun to kind of grow up with you. Like, I meet people before the show and after the show, and it’s so cool when...
text: It’s been really fun to kind of grow up with you. Like, I meet people before the show and after the show, and it’s so cool when someone will say ‘I’ve been listening to you since I was 12’ and they’re, like, a full adult. It’s also cool when someone says 'reputation is your first album that I bought.’ That’s awesome too. There’s no thing that you guys say to me that’s nice that I don’t appreciate. I appreciate it so much.
source: Taylor’s speech before Long Live in Seattle, Washington (May 22nd, 2018)
